title: Tulowitzki returns, AL East champ Blue Jays rally past Rays (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,015 Tulowitzki returns, AL East champ Blue Jays rally past Rays (Yahoo Sports) ST. PETERSBURG, Fla. (AP) -- Troy Tulowitzki doubled and singled in his return to the Toronto lineup after missing three weeks with injuries, and the AL East champion Blue Jays rallied past the Tampa Bay Rays 8-4 Friday night.
